The paper discusses the next generation of Vehicle-to-Vehicle (V2V) networks, which involves the integration of the millimeter wave band in vehicular operations. This topic falls under the category of Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the challenges and performance evaluation of the mmWave-specific V2V networks, which involves Information Theory (cs.IT), Multimedia (cs.MM), Systems and Control (cs.SY), and Cryptography and Security (cs.CR).
